# RWDD Assignment

## 💻 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (vanilla)
- PHP
- MySQL (with SQL stored in `/sql/database.sql`)

---

## 📁 Project Structure

📂 RWDD-Assignment/
│── 📂 public/
│   │── index.php              # Homepage (guest/user/admin sees diff content)
│   │── login.php
│   │── register.php
│   │── profile.php
│   │── events.php             # User: join/leave events, Admin: manage events
│   │── trading.php            # User: trade items, Admin: monitor/flag trades
│   │── communities.php        # User: post/comment, Admin: remove/report
│   │── assets/
│   │   ├── css/
│   │   ├── js/
│   │   └── images/
│   │── includes/
│   │   ├── header.php         # Dynamic navbar
│   │   └── footer.php
│
│── 📂 src/
│   │── db.php                 # Database connection
│   │── auth/                  # Login, register, logout
│   │── trading/               # Trade logic (requests, history, approvals if admin)
│   │── events/                # Event join/leave, admin moderation
│   │── communities/           # Posts/comments, admin moderation
│   │── notifications/         # QoL features (reminders, alerts)
│   │── utils/                 # Shared helpers (validators, session checks)
│
│── README.md
│── .gitignore
